{
  "_description": "告警卡片（红色 header + 故障详情 + 按钮组）。支持 Python 变量替换 {TITLE}/{SEVERITY}/{DESCRIPTION}/{TIME}/{BUTTON_URL}/{BUTTON_LABEL}。",
  "_usage": "把 JSON 用 Python json.load 后修改字段，再发出去。",
  "msg_type": "interactive",
  "card": {
    "config": {"wide_screen_mode": true},
    "header": {
      "title": {"content": "🚨 {TITLE}", "tag": "plain_text"},
      "template": "red"
    },
    "elements": [
      {"tag": "hr"},
      {
        "tag": "markdown",
        "content": "**告警等级：** <font color='red'>{SEVERITY}</font>\n**告警时间：** {TIME}\n**告警来源：** MiniMax 监控\n**Trace ID：** {TRACE_ID}"
      },
      {"tag": "hr"},
      {
        "tag": "markdown",
        "content": "**详情：**\n{DESCRIPTION}"
      },
      {
        "tag": "note",
        "elements": [
          {"tag": "plain_text", "content": "本卡片由 Hermes 飞书卡片工具自动发出"}
        ]
      },
      {
        "tag": "action",
        "actions": [
          {
            "tag": "button",
            "text": {"tag": "plain_text", "content": "📊 查看监控"},
            "type": "primary",
            "url": "{BUTTON_URL}"
          },
          {
            "tag": "button",
            "text": {"tag": "plain_text", "content": "✅ 认领处理"},
            "type": "default",
            "value": {"action": "ack", "alert_id": "{ALERT_ID}"}
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
